Append the following line to your .emacs file:

  (autoload 'csv-mode "csv-mode"
            "Major mode for editing comma-separated value files." t)
  (add-to-list 'auto-mode-alist '("\\.[Cc][Ss][Vv]\\'" . csv-mode))

